nope, i didn't die; i got a JOB!!  which, from a different angle, is prolly the same death sentence that i'd granted upon myself, but i must drop the whining coz CITIBANK's after my proletarian ass.  BILLS, BILLS, AND MORE BLASTED BILLS!  so what's a girl to do? werk it! WERRRK it, gurrrlll!!

speaking of WORK, my book backlog is another eternal busload of doorstops that just won't stop piling.  i can't get out of fullybooked or powerbooks without a purchase in tow!  i'm a shameless accumulator and my ability to devour books always gets trumped by that avaricious consumerist beast in me.  show me a previously out-of-print Palahniuk title, i sweat and hyperventillate like a pedophile in the middle of a packed preschool playground.  you get my point.

so uhh im still here, breathing, but STILL not debt relieved.

so here's BAHAY KUBO in gayspeak.


Valer kuberch, kahit jutay
Ang julamantrax donchi ay anek-anek.
Nyongkamas at nutring, nyogarilyas at kipay
Nyitaw, nyotaw, jutani.
Kundol, jutola, jupot jolabastrax
At mega join-join pa, jobanox nyustasa.
Nyubuyax, nyomatis, nyowang at luyax
And around the keme ay fulnes ng linga.
happiness is.... heaven is... and hey, its the motherfreaking princess's birthday! have a good one jack! and as they say, it aint gay till the balls touch! ;p

so Paris is free.

and in other not so new but considerably significant news (well, not really.), Rico Blanco is officially no longer with the band!  
yeah, Rivermaya!  no, silly! im not talking about those Muscle Marys who clock in at the gym daily and pump iron as if their herpes-infested colons depended on it!  but really, i cant stand those 'Stepford Faggot' types who act as if they mistake the multicolored radiance of a fabulous gay guy (namely ME!!) as an incubus of viral plague when, in unfortunate cases of temporal anomaly, the universe suddenly tasks one of those CLONES, of course bedecked in their generic metrosexual Maya schmaya fashion, to step on the fringes of my aura.  see, giving a wide berthing distance to a fella in this overpopulated metropolis is polite but blatant snobbery is *NOT*.  bitches, please!!  playing dead ignorant about my satin scarf'd existence doesnt break my crayons, NOoo! but brushing me off like im Jojo Veloso (or some suburban paedophile, for that matter!)?  TOO uncouth for my own good!!  come on, give your preppy Lacoste(?) things some kahihiyan!  coz i KNOW that you KNOW that Boy Abunda knows that you and i both bust our nuts thinking of Piolo (eew!) during lazy sunday nights and the cosmos decided to rain on your teaparty therefore, you're stuck in your bed and you start thinking where you stashed that porn mag!  i bet my hiv- ass that you and your straight-as-a-row-of-Veco-posts facade suck cock faster and harder than my blower can handle, yes?!  



forgive the digression.


it makes me sad sad sad when bands well, uhmm disband!  for the love of all things holy, just when they've broken out and carved a tiny little niche in the international scene, comes this fallout?!  


oh well, at least i cant blame my fancy scarves on this one.  
insane 12-year old gayboy out. ;p

like, Duh, right? and another bigger DUH!  as if you've not noticed, right?..
 
 
see, i need a boyfriend and lately, there's this boy, in the ghetto neyburhod, whom i've got the hots for since i moved in last year, who'd been bugging me or HAD me buggin'!  he's the usual brooding, salbahe type with the skinhead cut who clocks in at the neighborhood i.cafe day in, day out.  one of those "hey, i've just done college, my liver needs to die, haul in the next batch of red horse, pronto!!" professional bums (read: MY. FRIGGING. TYPE!!)!!  see, at first, we couldnt stand each other. or thought i couldnt.  and everytime we ran into each other, its always a race as to who bolts out first with a bitchface intact.  we'd been making deadma..OR lets rephrase that..HE'd been making deadma eversince and not until last week, when both of us figured in some sort of getting-to-know in the form of inuman sa kanto with his homies and i thought the 'deadma fest' between him and me was still in overdrive, when boyfriend suddenly, out of the dimness of the frontyard of our house, ASKED UNDER INFLUENCE, what my damage was and that if i had always had beef against him for treating him like shit ( or the lack thereof!) for the longest time.  but of course, that caught me and my gay fat ass offguard and i swear i thought my whole head glowed red from blushing ( thanks to our landlady, that tightwad of a hag, for swearing off verandah lighting altogether for the love of little green mangoes and therefore had lessened the night's embarassment!)  i swear to god, i devolved into a biological mass of Jell-O in front of the ONLY person i dont wanna embarrass myself with and quite surprised myself by gathering my mess and managing to reintroduce sense back to my system and told him, straightfaced, that i thought it was him who abhorred painfully flamboyant gayboys like ME!!  then boyfriend just gave me a cryptic "naa koy giampingan.."  whatthefuckity fuck, did he mean by zat?  GIAMPINGAN?  like what?....family jewels?  LOL.  but really, that got me thinking though (or sent me daydreaming!). 
 
 
and the asshole's been keeping my days occupied, eversince....well, daydreaming has, that is.
 
 
that boy.  shiiiiyyyaaattt!
 
 
oh, and did i say my hair was lavishly looong that night?? and YES i *did* manage to OUTSLUT myself, yet again!
 
 
ghetto pix comin' up.  delusional gayboy out!

GAY BOMB?!  THE PENTAGON?!  REALLY?!  FUCKING REALLY?!  LOL!

 

pentagon confirms it sought to build a 'gay bomb'

 

"....the ohio air force lab proposed that a bomb be developed that contained a chemical that would cause enemy soldiers to become gay, and to have their units break down because all their soldiers became irresistably attractive to one another," hammond said after reviewing the documents.

and traffic gets on my nerves and on everyoneelse's.  and apparently, the only way out of a gridlock is sitting through it and tuning it out with your trusty ipod while managing to transport yourself in a parallel universe where the yellow bird sings and the whiskey springs.  or find the nearest convenient diversion like say uhmm, cracking up at the ass face of the bloke sitting right across from you.  i know, mean, right?  but hey, its called self-preservation.  but NO, i havent been punched on the face or thrown overboard by some fugly passenger coz THIS has never failed to kill me everytime shit hits the fan on Gorordo ave:

...coz the devil wears prada. from carbon. Raquel Nacario is a general purpose evil-doer. She was created by God in 1979 (?) as my personal pain in the neck. The bane of my existence. She currently lives in Cebu, but has a summer residence down in Devil Gate Drive, aka South Cotabato. Im kidding.
hey, if you've got multiply, add me na!  Now na!

my cafe's closing.  it beats me why.  so im scrambling to drop a post.  i wanna RANT but im too time-restricted.  so here's a list..

1.  ruffa what's-her-face is all over tv these days.  bitch still got gorgeous hair. ive always envied those shampoo commercial models.  i wanna be like them when i grow up.  not in a creepy Stepford wife kind of way but i fancy KC ''so-what-if-i-have-cankles,-my-cheekbones-are-insured-for-a-million-pesos,-anyway!'' Concepcion's endorsements more.  me likey likey some waist length prostitute hair.  NOT.
 
2.  a newbie seatmate keeps on wedging her head behind my shoulder to 'eavesdrop' while im engaged in a call of duty.  'Vet?' she once asked.  'Sort of.' i snorted. 
 
3.  i wanna pack my bags and fly halfway around the world to take in salsa beats and booty-shake to the rituals of a Brazilian Carnaval in person.  im dying to. 
 

4.  just did two pending friendster invites.  aparently, we're still in this neverending quest to 'amass' more virtual friends and see who's the friendliest of them all.  ghea must have the downlow  why.

5.  its so uso magparehab sa US ngayon.  its hollyweird's publicity stunt du jour.  wala lang.  if you feel like checking into a facility, gimme a ring.  you know im such an attention-slut.

and the cafe's closing.  really.  ciao.

so 2 weeks into this one-cuppa-rice-a-day-oats-for-lunch-banana-and-crackers-in-between diet/ordeal and im still standing....as of yet.  see, this whole stress on my health was brought on since during the company's annual physical examinationsb the doctor had warned me of my BP bordering on the danger zone (which translates: im actually just one happy meal away from a stroke...or at least, keeling over from hyperventillation ..wait, arent those two precursors for   !).  see, my heart is pumping and sending blood, sloshing through my 23-year old arterial walls at 140 over 90 mm hg (its supposed to be read as 'torr', a unit of measuring pressure or something).  medically, that already qualifies as mild hypertension.. oh well, rajo laurel!  the sedentary lifestyle!  and please dont forget to give props to the fastfood diet!

what is pink, propped on a retro trike, disturbing with the swastika for a badge plus a gun as an accesory?  lookee lookee, it's Mark Ryden's little nazi boy painting aptly called "The Little Boy Blue"...

 

 
 
and i heart it as my headshot!  that spooky cold stare taking off from accusing blue eyes!!   i think he's cute like a periwinkle button, yes? no?

oh, well, this baby needs some pampering.

blurred clarity, what happened to you?!  did i scare you, hun?

thought so..

so i figured i only get to update my lj once a week.. well, im swamped with work and this is a good thing coz im not about to let go on the last strand of sanity my life is clinging to right now. *deep, deep sigh* i will not be insane. so, on to this psychotherapy... i just thought i let out the little (not really little!) zoolie in me. taken at some breakfast shop in I.T. park by raquel who might've cringed but this I-DONT-CARE-I-JUST-WANNA-BE-A-MODEL pose is for ghea! the reason ive become a vudu regular leans on the economic side- i have the VIP card..its soo cool i can step in with a maximum entourage of 10 dopeheads in tow for FREEEEEE with 15% discounts on drinks!!!!!!! so the democrats won. so what. yesterday was payday and since ive been performing insanely well (loser!)at work, paycheck's fatter. sweet. life is good.....when we're having fun!..BAMBINI! today's post is abysmally pointless.. abysmal...i sound so erudite. whatevs.

its the fourth time ive hauled my ass to the restrooms to puke my guts out..

2 redhorse stallions and a few cocktail shots ago, raquel and i found ourselves whoring at the vudu mezzanine bar with lit marlborro reds in tow..  no, im not being fancy-for crying out loud, its the only decent club we could allow ourselves to marinate with house music for our own good.  

so, i dont know what the whole point of this is..  all i know is, i gave somebody head last night which counts to nothing coz the whole necking that led to that got trampled upon by me being a stinking bacchanalian who doesnt give two flying figs if i scored or not, coz getting high on alcohol and a dash of post-teen rage trumps cumming and getting arsed ANYTIME! 

so, ive been reading a lot of RAGE-inducing literary stuff and getting lost in those books, pilfered or bought, is my new-found addiction..  it sounds so phony but ive been flipping the bird..

home sucks...i got home last thursday and i oughta be back in cebu ryt now and its supposed to be my first day of my work week but i, having gone on standby mode for a fully booked trip back to cebu from bumfuck maasin proved to be worthless, hopeless and drop dead exhausting, like literally...so, back to homebase was where ive ended up in, wearing a loser face for not snagging a friggin return seat and tried to content myself to be resigned to the fact that an issued warning for my fucked up schedule adherence is in the works..work sucks major balls alotatimes you know..

anywho, my whole VACA has just been all about fucking up my liver...i hate it coz im supposed to be older and i know im older and all ive been doing is douche my throat with red horse or anything thats threatening to my liver's health..gawd..

my father wants me to chip in the whole installment-payment-for-the-new-motorcycle thing...im not really liking the idea even if he promised it'll all be under my name and that i could always have it everytime i get home, but fuck, i dont like its paint.

like, my head will be next on the chopping board for going on a NO-CALL-NO-SHOW on my job..idk.

hey..i have no words to say..i mean, being figuratively dead for a long time which means not being able to check on my eljay friends' posts and post(!!!),for crying out loud, for like aeons is SO lame of me!  

my ephemeral lj existence..

in other news, im just digging Marquis de Sade's works for now! like,**vomits**, im such a pretentious fucker pretending to be intellectual and all!!  anywho, since i admire my french buddy Sade here, i guess, its contingent that i be called a Sadist!  

to qoute the philosoPERVE's last will and testament:

"Imperious, choleric, irascible, extreme in everything, with a dissolute imagination the like of which has never been seen, atheistic to the point of fanaticism, there you have me in a nutshell.... Kill me again or take me as I am, for I shall not change."

He also coined this---> Sex without pain is like food without taste....go figure!! *weg*



im starved and my supe is looking daggers!wehehehe..im wasting my office's internet hours!!  woohoo!!

anywho, yeah, im sick in the head and i might just be back!!

and yeah, That's all!  i just cant get over Meryll Streep's Miranda Priestly character's icy cold stares!!ahlavettt!!

shit.  i've never experienced mactan waters until yesterday!  like, omg, im gonna have leatherface when i reach 30 or sumth..  i dont know if the spf 6 worked but i sure loved how the sun did some damage to my skin, i mean, tanning, i'd like to think...  shit,you guys, the salt water is like so SALTY..hehe..  i dont know, after emerging from the water for like 5 minutes, i started seeing like, traces of powdery salt on my arms and earlobes..THAT concentrated!  CAMWHORAGE evidence, soon!

pulled up an all-nighter.  got pissdrunk.  vandalized, no, scrap that! did some major graffiti on my buddy's pad's freshly-painted walls after marinating our poor livers with the same old, same old potion.  moshed in a makeshift pit, taking in House like noobs in the midst of a party peopled by hulking faggots-on-steroids.  got all too wet, we decided to call it a night er, an early morning.  got locked out.  broke in...only to find our pickled selves in the swelter of this annexed room.  stripped off to our undies to nurse our body temps.  passed out.


life as it should be.

captain jack is back!!  but miss zafra is not so impressed.  im regretting i checked that gargoyle of a writer's blog today.  see, i've been fired up with this sequel eversince its announcement, and now this buzzkill of a review?!  well, i already booked my sureseats ticket.  so, im hoping for the best and orlando bloom's bahama-tanned bum. :)  i just wish no rowdy kids on a last full show this time coz they oughta be squeezing their moms' udders or sumth.  

in other news, its PAYDAY this friday!!  NIKOOON motherfucker, i invoke the power of your anus to hatch up some alcohol-fuelled wreckage!  dude, i want PAKING BEER and HOT poor ass COLLEGE BOYS who'll suck up on my wishes at the mere sight of my crisp cabbage!  eeeeww!  im starting to sound like a leather-faced,stone-aged GAYLORD! *shudders*

that could be me, so punk.

ugh.  im jealous, no, more like fiercely envious at the sight of world travelers converging in one great party that is Copa Mundial rolling its last week (?) in germany!  sheesh. i wanna travel like those rabid fans clad in each of their country's colors!  see, unlike those nomads streetpartying in germany, screaming their lungs till their eyes pop out from their sockets, im taking calls and cursing and spitting vitriolic statements at rejected fliers, unhappy hotel guests, and all those dark and bitching creatures while on mute!  not so fun.  GERMANYYYYYYYYYY!  somebody buy me a 1-way flight to Munich!  we'll use my IATA travel agent discount card and sway the Lufthansa airlines' powers-that-be for you to get discount,too and ill hoard peanut brittle by crates for in-flight munchies.

i just wanna earn miles, is that too much to ask? :(

i went straight to rob's place after my officemates stood me up for our supposed pig-out session.  so cruel.  but, its a good thing i had an alternate itinerary which was to bargain hunt for books. hehehe.  so, i hauled my food-deprived ass (thank god!) to the mall and checked this fab corner selling semi-used books at staggering discounts!  so, i went in to browse.  went to my fave Patricia Cornwell section but Doctor Kay didnt have anything new to offer other than dead victims' corpses slated for autopsy and same old same old psycho gore.  the store owner who doubles as the cashier/bagger noticed me hovering on the corner and hailed and hollered - books just in!!  the pile was mostly Dan Brownian crap and some ny times bestsellers but sumth glinted from among the pile.  it was golden and screaming.  i picked it up coz it was golden and screaming! hah!  it was Ian Caldwell's and Dustin Thomason's first novel,   The Rule of Four. that shit was New York Times bestseller for six months dude and the gracious store owner offered it for 200 flippin pesos and amazon sells it at $16.32 right now! go, figure!  im a happy camper.

i finally got to haul my ass to the movies and catch the blue, padded spandex(?)-clad,red-caped long-distance flier last night.  the 2-hour and 45-minute flick did not disappoint but ayala cinemas should better impose viewing hours for motherfucking kids!  gawd, they were everywhere.  i was fine until this fatherly-looking person asked me to move my ass like 3 seats over so that his whole family of 8 could be seated together.  bummer.  his kids were actually complaining about lapsitting so that was root of my plight.  but, almighty god!!it was the last full show and those kids were supposed to be sucking breasts!  but i decided to "take" in the flick and stop bitching!  even though the padded suit was pretty obvious in some scenes, Brandon Routh still managed to ooze with superman juices making me cream my pants.  and Parker Posey didnt disappoint too!  she's very good with these "character" roles!  she IS the shiznit, scrap that, an ICON!   i've loved her since SUBURBIA!

the ride home was a bitch too!  i felt like a butch-looking whore with my big mickey mouse shirt on, waiting for that downtown ride beside TJ's.  i felt like i've spent much for the day, so the minimum 6-peso return fare, i thought, was in order.  but, after what seemed like a whole larvae-metamorphose-to-butterfly life cycle,  i ended up hailin a cab.  

and, yah, the cabbie, for lacking loose change, charged me more.
